OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782370083
OL,3,CAustralian officially becomes world's
OL,4,Cloudest person at 122 decibels
OL,6,FAn Australian man has officially been
OL,7,Fcrowned the world's loudest person
OL,8,Fafter shouting "now" at 122.4 decibels.
OL,10,FThat's similar in noise level to a
OL,11,Fchain saw, a jet aircraft taking off
OL,12,For an ambulance siren at close range.
OL,14,FJoseph McGrail-Bateup, a professional
OL,15,Fair conditioner cleaner and honourary
OL,16,Ftown crier, said the feat was not
OL,17,Fsomething he could train for.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
