FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782370083
OL,3,CAustralian officially becomes world's
OL,4,Cloudest person at 122 decibels
OL,6,F"There's no way that you can actually
OL,7,Fpractise for it. You have to just keep
OL,8,Fit for the day, especially with the
OL,9,Fworld record attempt," he said.
OL,11,FWatch as Joseph McGrail-Bateup
OL,12,Fshatters the Guinness World Record for
OL,13,Floudest shout by an individual
OL,15,F"It took me seven attempts just for
OL,16,Fone word, which was the word 'now',
OL,17,Fand my voice was shot for the next
OL,18,Fcouple of days as well.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@VO]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,320,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782370083
OL,3,CAustralian officially becomes world's
OL,4,Cloudest person at 122 decibels
OL,6,F"It was husky. It was terrible. So no,
OL,7,Fyou can't really practise for it. But
OL,8,Fit's a lot of fun when you're doing
OL,9,Fit."
OL,11,FThe 58-year-old broke the previous
OL,12,Frecord of 121.7 decibels set by
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland schoolteacher
OL,14,FAnnalisa Flanagan in 1994. She had
OL,15,Fyelled an ear-piercing "quiet!".
OL,17,FMr McGrail-Bateup considered himself
OL,18,Fthe world's loudest man rather than
OL,19,Fthe loudest person, he said. There was
OL,20,Fno previous record for the loudest man.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@DO]wD@XOUwD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
