PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782370083
OL,3,CAustralian officially becomes world's
OL,4,Cloudest person at 122 decibels
OL,6,F"I'm pleased that she (Flanagan) gets
OL,7,Fto keep her record. So she's still the
OL,8,Floudest woman in the world and I'm the
OL,9,Floudest male in the world," he said.
OL,11,FHe became competitively loud when he
OL,12,Fwas appointed the official town crier
OL,13,Fof the national capital Canberra in
OL,14,F2017.
OL,16,FIt's an honourary and part-time role
OL,17,Festablished by the local government
OL,18,Fwhich he considers "a bit of fun". His
OL,19,Ftown crier name is Lord Joseph, and he
OL,20,Fmakes announcements at community
OL,21,Fevents, school fetes and car shows.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@[O]zD@TOUzD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
