PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782370083
OL,3,CAustralian officially becomes world's
OL,4,Cloudest person at 122 decibels
OL,6,FWith the job came membership of the
OL,7,FAncient and Honorable Guild of
OL,8,FAustralian Town Criers, a competitive
OL,9,Fprofessional organisation dedicated to
OL,10,Fpreserving members' historic and
OL,11,Fceremonial roles.
OL,13,FHe won a 2024 guild competition with
OL,14,Fthe loudest "Oyez, Oyez, Oyez" at 98
OL,15,Fdecibels. That was a command for
OL,16,Fsilence and attention before a town
OL,17,Fcrier makes a proclamation.
OL,19,FMr McGrail-Bateup experimented with
OL,20,Fseveral words for his world record
OL,21,Fattempt before settling on "now".
OL,26,@vD@MOUvD@^O]}D@\OU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
