PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782370083
OL,3,CAustralian officially becomes world's
OL,4,Cloudest person at 122 decibels
OL,6,FHis shout was recorded May 2 in a
OL,7,FCanberra radio studio by a
OL,8,Fprofessional acoustic engineer and
OL,9,Fwith witnesses present. The files were
OL,10,Fsent to Guinness World Records, who
OL,11,Flater confirmed the record.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,FIt's the second time McGrail-Bateup
OL,19,Fhas broken a world record.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
