OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1782370083
OL,3,CAustralian officially becomes world's
OL,4,Cloudest person at 122 decibels
OL,6,FIn 2019, he broke a speed record for
OL,7,Fan archer shooting 10 arrows. His time
OL,8,Fof 60.03 seconds shaved a fraction of
OL,9,Fa second off a record that had stood
OL,10,Fsince 2015.
OL,12,FNine months later, a seven-year-old
OL,13,Fboy shattered McGrail-Bateup's record
OL,14,Fby 11.4 seconds.
OL,16,FMcGrail-Bateup wasn't interested in
OL,17,Fattempting to regain the archery
OL,18,Frecord or in keeping his shouting
OL,19,Frecord.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
